1.name: Mininja's Paw
1.desc: Easier to roll medium snowballs when equipped, but with limited speed. Grants additional big snowball(s) in Bowling mode.

2.name: Me-Yow's Paw
2.desc: Easier to roll large snowballs when equipped, and with increased speed too. Grants additional fast snowball(s) in Bowling mode.

3.name: Mitir's Paw
3.desc: Has a chance to refresh skills after use when equipped. Grants additional small snowball(s) in Bowling mode.
